        <div><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> <blockquote><font face="Verdana" size=2 color="#050056">Sponsored by Faydwer's Brethren Guild<br>Date: Sunday, September 3rd<br>Time: 8:00pm Eastern, 7:00pm Central, 6:00pm Mountain and 5:00pm Pacific<br><br>To all citizens of Norrath: A Faydwer's Brethren Guild Event will be held for all player's of the younger season at the lift near the Priest of Discord in Kelethin. Faydwer's Brethren, a guild made up of the citizens of Faydwer is dedicated to roleplay. We will help new players in learning to play Everquest. We will assist in your fight against the denizens of Greater Faydark, and answer questions regarding the realms, your professions (class), and strategies.<br><br>Activities will include small scale adventures, discussions of your choosing, contests and prizes. Please join us all new citizens to the lands of Norrath on Bertoxxulous. Faydwer's Brethren will be there.<br><br>Please check out the following site for information about us:<br><a href="http://members.aol.com/ShadowDragon7/EverQuest"target="_blank">http://members.aol.com/ShadowDragon7/EverQuest</a><br><br>Warm Regards,<br>Vdayan Windrider, Bard of Kelethin<br>Guild Leader of Faydwer's Brethren</font></blockquote> </font> 
