        <div><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> This was submitted by Hendershot<br><br><blockquote><font face="Verdana" size=2 color="#050056">Oothomp Boro (Troll) accompanied by a pair of vicious wolves (Snarrl and Wooff) hijacked the bridge into North Karana this evening in East Karana. He was demanding 5 shiny yellow coins to pass and would kill whoever wouldnt pass. <br><br>He was relentless in killing a several people who refused to pay untill A Dark Elf Necro showed up. He wasnt about to pay the toll and a fight seemed to start but the DE feared the troll away and the cround broke out in laughter. <br><br>Soon after a reinforcements showed up. A battle cry was sounded and everyone in the zone ran and started attacking him from all sides, finishing him quickly and slaying his pets. We cheered, it was cool. Random GM event I assume.<br><br>Started about 11pm Pacific<br>Yielded a Spiked Collar, Blackened Iron Leggings and a 2h Hammer<br><br>Hendershot<br>Level 19 Warrior of Morrel Thule<br>Proud Member of Praesul</font></blockquote><br><br>Come see screenshots of the event <a href="http://boards.stratics.com/cgi-bin/boards/eq/showflat.pl?Cat=7,8,9,10,11&Board=eqpictures&Number=377933&page=0&view=collapsed&sb=5"target="_blank">here</a> in the <a href="http://eq.stratics.com/content/forums/pictures.html"target="_blank">EQSS Pictures Forum</a> </font> 
