    <td><font color="050056" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><b>New At Stratics</b></font> 
      <div><font color="#660000" size="1" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b>Stratics_Network_Announcement 
        [ 6:45 AM EDT ] -</b></font><font color="ff0000" size="1" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"> 
        <a href="mailto:greebo@stratics.com?subject=EQNews">Greebo</a></font> 
        <div><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> <blockquote><font face="verdana" size=2 color=#050056><p>Here's a quick look at what's new to the Stratics Network this week:<br><p><b>Stratics House of Commons This Week</b><br><ul><li><a href="http://at.stratics.com/sections/community/hoc.shtml">Atriarch House of Commons</a>: This Tuesday, August 29th, at 7pm CST in <a href="http://at.stratics.com/sections/community/irc1.shtml">#athoc</a>. Lead Designer Serefina will be onhand to answer all your questions about the Lokai, the game's newest species.</li><br><li><a href="http://uohoc.stratics.com/">Origin House of Commons</a>: This Wednesday, August 30th, at 7pm CST in <a href="http://uo2.stratics.com/sections/tools/irc.shtml">#uwohoc</a>. The Origin design team will be here to answer your questions about the development of this groundbreaking game. No topic has yet been set.</li></ul><br><p>To access Stratics IRC, simply connect to one of the following servers than join the appropriate HOC channel.<br><ul><li>compu.stratics.com</li><br><li>dhp.stratics.com</li><br><li>frws.stratics.com</li><br><li>intworks.stratics.com</li></ul>  <br><p><a href="http://ad.stratics.com"><b> Adellion Stratics</b></a><br><ul><li><a href="http://ad.stratics.com/">Adellion Stratics</a> has a new <a href="http://ad.stratics.com/cgi-bin/databases/devmusings/db.cgi?db=default&uid=default&view_records=1&sb=4&so=descend&ID=*">Developer Quotes Database</a>. Now you can refer back to everything the Adellion developers have to say, and get a good understanding of everything about Adellion.</li></ul> <br><p><a href="http://ao.stratics.com"><b>Anarchy Online Stratics</b></a><br><ul><li>Beta testing phase 2 has been launched! Have you dropped by <a href="http://ao.stratics.com">AOS</a> lately and filled out your application? There's just 1 more phase left!</li> <br><li>The AOS <a href="http://ao.stratics.com/sections/contest/bannercontest.shtml"">Advertisement and Guild Banner Contest</a> ends Thursday! Be sure to drop by and submit an entry.<br></li></ul><br><p><a href="http://ac.stratics.com"><b>Asheron's Call Stratics</b></a>  <br><ul><li>Another new quest guide for your delectation: <a href="http://ac.stratics.com/content/quests/colier/colier.shtml">The Baron of Colier's Life Giving Amulet</a>.</li><br><li>Plus,some enhancements to the <a href="http://ac.stratics.com/content/statistics/magic/magic.shtml">Spell database</a>.</li></ul><br><p><a href="http://at.stratics.com"><b>Atriarch Stratics</b></a><br><ul><li>This coming Tuesday, August 29th at 8pm Eastern Standard Time is the next <a href="http://at.stratics.com/sections/community/hoc.shtml">Atriarch House of Commons</a> chat! <a href="http://at.stratics.com/sections/community/irc1.shtml">#athoc</a> on Stratics IRC will play host to the Atriarch dev team, including our favorite IRC pal, Serafina Pechan. This time we'll be discussing the Lokai species, so explorers and adventurers come one, come all!. Just in case you haven't seen the Lokai Species Profile, be sure to check it out now. Get your questions ready and come prepared to hear some great new information!</li></ul><br><p><a href="http://eq.stratics.com"><b>EverQuest Stratics</b></a><br><ul><li>Be sure to join <a href="http://eq.stratics.com/content/irc/">#everquest</a> for the lastest Everquest chat!</li></ul><br><p><a href="http://hj.stratics.com"><b>Hero's Journey Stratics</b></a><br><ul><li>Wake yourself up this Monday morning with HJS's <a href="http://hj.stratics.com/lore/editorials/editorials.html">Editorials</a>.</li><br><li>Or dive into the game design discussion on the <a href="http://boards.stratics.com/cgi-bin/forums/wwwthreads.pl?Cat=12">HJS forums</a>.</li></ul><br><p><a href="http://jg.stratics.com"><b>Jumpgate Stratics</b></a><br><ul><li><a href="http://jg.stratics.com/sections/sod/archives.shtml">New Screenshots</a> from Pre-Release are being added to JumpGate Stratics daily.</li><br><li>We will be holding our <a href="http://jg.stratics.com/sections/jghoc/jghoc.shtml">Second JumpGate House of Commons</a> on Tuesday, September 18, at 7pm CST in channel #jghoc on Stratics IRC.</li></ul><br><p><a href="http://nwn.stratics.com"><b>Neverwinter Stratics</b></a><br><p>The revamping of the Neverwinter Nights Stratics site is almost complete, a few more tweaks and adjustments and it will be ready for prime time!<br><p>What will the revamp of the site bring?<br><ul><li>A better menu system that is easier to navigate</li><br><li>A more organized layout to the site so things are easier to find<br><li>And it paves the way for the new content we are working on for your enjoyment!</li></ul><br><p>Look for the announcement of the revamped site soon!<br><p><a href="http://uo2.stratics.com"><b>Origin Stratics</b></a><br><ul><li>We are pleased to announce our 2nd ORIGIN House of Commons scheduled for Wednesday, August 30th, at 7pm CST in <a href="http://uo2.stratics.com/sections/tools/irc.shtml">#uwohoc</a>. Members of the design team for Ultima Worlds Online:ORIGIN will be onhand to answer your questions. The topic will be General Discussion. </li><br><li>Interested in finding out more on the cultures and groups being developed for ORIGIN to make it not just a game, but a living and breathing world? Then make sure to head on over to our brand new <a href="http://uo2.stratics.com/sections/gameplay/cultures.shtml">Cultures Section</a> to read about The House of the Griffin, The Shadow Hunters, The Technocrats, and many others. </li></ul><br><p><a href="http://uo.stratics.com"><b>Ultima-Online Stratics</b></a><br><ul><li>Not new at all, but interesting nevertheless. Come visit the <a href="http://uodr.stratics.com/ideas/board.html">Ideas Den</a> where our readers can post ideas on improving UO and other readers can vote on these ideas. Ideas that get lots of votes are promoted to the <a href="http://uodr.stratics.com/cgi-bin/ideas/denindex.pl?action=hall">Ideas Hall</a> and the ideas that our readers voted for the most are promoted to the <a href="http://uodr.stratics.com/cgi-bin/ideas/denindex.pl?action=fame">Ideas Hall of Fame</a>. The Ideas Den is the best way to share your ideas and find out what the rest of the UO Community thinks of them.</li></ul></blockquote> </font> 
